WEBVTT

27:56.024 --> 27:57.316
You could've stayed for dinner.

27:57.316 --> 27:59.149
No.
I have a client meeting at 8:30.

27:59.608 --> 28:02.483
I rushed here only
because it was this matter.

28:02.524 --> 28:03.608
At such short notice.

28:03.733 --> 28:04.858
Must have been
a lot of trouble, right?
